snippet.title: City Planner Plays
snippet.description:
Ever wonder what an Urban Planner does for fun?  Well, they play City Builders of course!  I have loved City Builders since I was a kid and have been playing them for as long as I can remember.  I started out with the original SimCity on the SNES, graduated to SimCity 2000 on the PC, and have played every City Builder I can since then.

Join me and see how my planning experience has influenced the way I play City Builders!

Let's chat on Discord!  http://discord.gg/cityplannerplays

Want to support the channel?  Here's how you can help:
- Buy a Steam Key through my store: https://www.nexus.gg/CityPlannerPlays
- Support me on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/CityPlannerPlays
- Get some Merch - https://city-planner-plays.myteespring.co/

Email is for business inquiries only and all other emails will be extremely delayed and/or missed.  If you want to chat with me, @me on my Discord server!  I'm on there nearly everyday.
